Detailed Description

AT32UC3C UC3C_EK board header file.

This file contains definitions and services related to the features of the UC3C_EK board.

To use this board, define BOARD=UC3C_EK.

  • Compiler: IAR EWAVR32 and GNU GCC for AVR32
  • Supported devices: All AVR32 AT32UC3C devices can be used.
  • AppNote:
Author:
Atmel Corporation: http://www.atmel.com
Support and FAQ: http://support.atmel.no/
